{"tid":291804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅磡劏房黃雨塌露台 嚇煞街坊半夜逃命","createTime":"2017-06-21T00:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T06:09:39.000Z","uid":58669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c53a1135173df784345d85997efdc806edafdf71","tid":291804,"uid":58669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170621/_2017062106431034176.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170621%2F_2017062106431034176.jpeg&h=d41b9920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170621/_2017062106432759777.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170621%2F_2017062106432759777.jpeg&h=612f59aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170621/_2017062106433692197.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170621%2F_2017062106433692197.jpeg&h=588f8431&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n凌晨時份本港受暴雨侵襲，天文台一度發出黃雨警告，及後2時45分才取消。但期間發生驚險一幕，紅磡機利士南路50號的劏房唐樓，懷疑因不勝雨水狂打，露台突然崩塌，警方在黃雨中要疏散20多人，及封閉現場，消防員在場戒備。<br />\n<br />\n事發位置為二樓單位，露台面積約2米乘4米，意外後部份石屎仍在半空。據悉唐樓多用作劏房，經已成為發展商收購目標，但七層中2、3及5樓仍有人居住。事發劏房內的床舖等雜物連同露台全部塌至地下。"},{"pid":"2411b6dbf65a358dd92435b4b1c1cd861f2a7991","tid":291804,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:54:28.000Z","msg":"嗰一帶都係玄牛收樓範圍喎🙊"},{"pid":"8dc49c01a6186e16aad330f65feb19daecc75f2d","tid":291804,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:09:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bb4b489ec277410f0ea868123252372c2b659ee","tid":291804,"uid":864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:11:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓訓下跣咗落樓都咪話唔講得笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係都唔出街又點仆街啊？"},{"pid":"febbd8b0f0dcf86fdf0b0b8ea0e53ea9eb7bfa75","tid":291804,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:15:16.000Z","msg":"變危樓"},{"pid":"16eb35db55c3b56cf9c7439499d790f583300f34","tid":291804,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:17:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓訓下跣咗落樓都咪話唔講得笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要為發夢啦  仆街 點知真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3908d8c1130d441754f0c6a51a1cc065e125b4a7","tid":291804,"uid":58669,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓訓下跣咗落樓都咪話唔講得笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/h006/h93/img201102180205000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.singtao.ca%2Ftoronto%2Fh006%2Fh93%2Fimg201102180205000.jpg&h=870a64e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24a439eefe273818cc36f11b99c51e29041d9976","tid":291804,"uid":7673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:24:53.000Z","msg":"痴撚線好在無人行過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e501a3ddf93a5df2fe7288b4a090168cac8d41","tid":291804,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:28:18.000Z","msg":"呢排一直落雨會唔會愈塌愈多"},{"pid":"62a265f74e9d66cf72642c15797b2f855ad6b8e5","tid":291804,"uid":106482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:32:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>訓訓下跣咗落樓都咪話唔講得笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/h006/h93/img201102180205000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.singtao.ca%2Ftoronto%2Fh